http://tinyurl.com/8xchn

http://store.yahoo.com/eagleday/whac2.html
http://store.yahoo.com/eagleday/potiac.html

These units are reasonably priced and let you bleed the excess from the tire
until they read correctly. The BMW version is more motorcycle friendly (90
degree fitting).

